	{"x4pointer":" "
	 ,"x4code":null
	,"x4freetext":["The primary 15N beam with an energy of 49.7 A MeV was"
		,"focused on the production 9Be target. The secondary"
		,"beam of fragmentation reaction products was formed"
		,"and purified by the magnetic system of the fragment"
		,"separator."]
	}
      ]
